<h2 id="exceptions">Exceptions</h2>

<p>Code exceptions and errors not expressable via HTTP-Status codes are responded in the response body.
The error object contains a <var>Code</var>, <var>Message</var> and a <var>Type</var>.</p>

<pre>
{
	"error": {
		"code": 1234,
		"message": "Invalid Credentials",
		"type": "\keeko\core\exceptions\InvalidCredentialsException"
	}
}
</pre>

